    product or service.

(b) No Third-Party Redistribution. You may not publish, upload, or distribute
    the Software (or any modified version) on package managers, software
    distribution platforms, or repositories such as PyPI, Homebrew, apt, dnf,
    npm, Docker Hub, or similar. Only the Copyright Holder, or third parties
